<s> As reported by Glenn Adams: "In DM3, the invocation of the submit() method causes the firing of the ONSUBMIT event prior to performing its intended semantics, and, if the event returns a value that is equivalent (coercable) to FALSE, then those intended semantics (form submission) are ignored."  </s>
